The '''2012 French Road Cycling Cup''' was the 21st edition of the [[French Road Cycling Cup]] and was won by [[Samuel Dumoulin]].
Compared to the previous edition, two new events were added to the calendar, namely the [[Classic Loire Atlantique]] and the [[Route Adélie]]. The defending champion from [[2011 French Road Cycling Cup|2011]] was [[Tony Gallopin]].
