'''Association Sportive Tanda''', more commonly known as '''AS Tanda''' or just '''Tanda''', is an [[Côte d'Ivoire|Ivorian]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Tanda, Ivory Coast|Tanda]] in the [[Gontougo Region]].<ref>https://int.soccerway.com/teams/cote-divoire/tanda/25666/</ref>

They are a member of the [[Fédération Ivoirienne de Football]] Premiere Division.

==Stadium==
Currently the team plays at the 3000 capacity [[Stade Henri Konan Bédié]].

==League participations==
*'''[[Côte d'Ivoire Premier Division]]: 2013–.
*'''[[Ligue 2 (Ivory Coast)]]: ?-2013.

