'''Serinevler Athletics Stadium''' ({{lang-tr|Serinevler Atletizm Pisti}}) is a sports venue for [[athletics (sport)|athletics]] competitions in [[track and field]] located in [[Yüreğir]], [[Adana]].<ref>http://adana.gsb.gov.tr/HaberDetaylari/1/14430/23-yasalti-atletizm-sampiyonasi.aspx</ref>
