'''Suan Sunandha Rajabhat University Salaya Campus Stadium''' ({{lang-th|สนาม มรภ.สวนสุนันทา ศาลายา}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Nakhon Pathom Province]], [[Thailand]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. The stadium holds 3,000 people.
{{coord|13.867954|100.270395 |type:landmark_region:TH|display=title}}
